			<title>Copying_Is_Not_Theft.mp3</title>
			<creator>Nina Paley</creator>
			<album>Copying is not Theft</album>
			<trackNum>1</trackNum>
			<annotation>The song &quot;Copying is not Theft&quot; from Nina Paley, a song that questions copyright, and backs up the fact that copying is not theft, and theft is a smear word when it comes to copying files. The cartoon takes Disney styling to mock Disneys abuse of copyright, and to make the song more recognizable and notable.</annotation>
