			<trackNum>1</trackNum>
			<annotation>The first and main song of Tiny Tower. Unless in the Halloween or Christmas seasons, this song is the first one in the loop of in-game background music. It is also the default background song in Lego Tower. As of 2022 January 30th, it is used in no other NimbleBit Games. Composed by Dan Foster of NimbleBit LLC.</annotation>
